---
import Layout from '../../layouts/Layout.astro';
import Navigation from '../../components/Navigation.astro';
import Footer from '../../components/Footer.astro';
---

<Layout title="Product Management Training - SP Consulting">
  <Navigation />
  
  <main class="pt-20">
    <section class="bg-primary text-white py-20">
      <div class="container mx-auto px-4">
        <h1 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-bold mb-6">Product Management Training</h1>
        <p class="text-xl">Master non-software product development across five essential domains</p>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="py-20">
      <div class="container mx-auto px-4 max-w-4xl">
        <div class="space-y-16">
          <div>
            <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold mb-6">Training Modules</h2>
            <div class="space-y-8">
              <!-- Introduction Module -->
              <div class="bg-white p-8 rounded-lg shadow-lg">
                <div class="flex items-start gap-6 mb-6">
                  <div class="bg-primary/10 p-3 rounded-lg">
                    <svg class="w-8 h-8 text-primary" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                      <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M12 6.253v13m0-13C10.832 5.477 9.246 5 7.5 5S4.168 5.477 3 6.253v13C4.168 18.477 5.754 18 7.5 18s3.332.477 4.5 1.253m0-13C13.168 5.477 14.754 5 16.5 5c1.747 0 3.332.477 4.5 1.253v13C19.832 18.477 18.247 18 16.5 18c-1.746 0-3.332.477-4.5 1.253"/>
                    </svg>
                  </div>
                  <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold">Introduction to Product Management</h3>
                </div>
                <p class="text-gray-600 mb-6">
                  Understand the product manager's role at the intersection of business, technology, and user experience in hardware contexts.
                </p>
                <ul class="space-y-3 text-gray-600 mb-6">
                  <li>• Master product lifecycle management principles</li>
                  <li>• Learn effective cross-functional collaboration</li>
                  <li>• Distinguish between product and project management roles</li>
                  <li>• Navigate hardware-specific challenges</li>
                </ul>
                <p class="text-sm text-gray-500">Duration: 2 days</p>
              </div>

              <!-- Market Module -->
              <div class="bg-white p-8 rounded-lg shadow-lg">
                <div class="flex items-start gap-6 mb-6">
                  <div class="bg-primary/10 p-3 rounded-lg">
                    <svg class="w-8 h-8 text-primary" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                      <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M9 19v-6a2 2 0 00-2-2H5a2 2 0 00-2 2v6a2 2 0 002 2h2a2 2 0 002-2zm0 0V9a2 2 0 012-2h2a2 2 0 012 2v10m-6 0a2 2 0 002 2h2a2 2 0 002-2m0 0V5a2 2 0 012-2h2a2 2 0 012 2v14a2 2 0 01-2 2h-2a2 2 0 01-2-2z"/>
                    </svg>
                  </div>
                  <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold">Understanding the Market</h3>
                </div>
                <p class="text-gray-600 mb-6">
                  Learn methodologies for market research, competitive analysis, and opportunity identification in hardware markets.
                </p>
                <ul class="space-y-3 text-gray-600 mb-6">
                  <li>• Conduct comprehensive market research</li>
                  <li>• Analyze industry trends and competition</li>
                  <li>• Develop strategic product positioning</li>
                  <li>• Identify market opportunities</li>
                </ul>
                <p class="text-sm text-gray-500">Duration: 3 days</p>
              </div>

              <!-- Customer Problem Module -->
              <div class="bg-white p-8 rounded-lg shadow-lg">
                <div class="flex items-start gap-6 mb-6">
                  <div class="bg-primary/10 p-3 rounded-lg">
                    <svg class="w-8 h-8 text-primary" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                      <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M18.364 5.636l-3.536 3.536m0 5.656l3.536 3.536M9.172 9.172L5.636 5.636m3.536 9.192l-3.536 3.536M21 12a9 9 0 11-18 0 9 9 0 0118 0zm-5 0a4 4 0 11-8 0 4 4 0 018 0z"/>
                    </svg>
                  </div>
                  <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold">Customer Problem Identification</h3>
                </div>
                <p class="text-gray-600 mb-6">
                  Master techniques for uncovering genuine user needs through research and analysis.
                </p>
                <ul class="space-y-3 text-gray-600 mb-6">
                  <li>• Create hardware-specific user personas</li>
                  <li>• Develop detailed journey maps</li>
                  <li>• Craft effective problem statements</li>
                  <li>• Validate user pain points</li>
                </ul>
                <p class="text-sm text-gray-500">Duration: 2 days</p>
              </div>

              <!-- Strategic Alignment Module -->
              <div class="bg-white p-8 rounded-lg shadow-lg">
                <div class="flex items-start gap-6 mb-6">
                  <div class="bg-primary/10 p-3 rounded-lg">
                    <svg class="w-8 h-8 text-primary" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                      <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M9 19v-6a2 2 0 00-2-2H5a2 2 0 00-2 2v6a2 2 0 002 2h2a2 2 0 002-2zm0 0V9a2 2 0 012-2h2a2 2 0 012 2v10m-6 0a2 2 0 002 2h2a2 2 0 002-2m0 0V5a2 2 0 012-2h2a2 2 0 012 2v14a2 2 0 01-2 2h-2a2 2 0 01-2-2z"/>
                    </svg>
                  </div>
                  <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold">Strategic Alignment</h3>
                </div>
                <p class="text-gray-600 mb-6">
                  Learn techniques for ensuring product initiatives support organizational objectives.
                </p>
                <ul class="space-y-3 text-gray-600 mb-6">
                  <li>• Master stakeholder management</li>
                  <li>• Develop compelling business cases</li>
                  <li>• Optimize resource allocation</li>
                  <li>• Secure executive support</li>
                </ul>
                <p class="text-sm text-gray-500">Duration: 1 day</p>
              </div>

              <!-- MVP Module -->
              <div class="bg-white p-8 rounded-lg shadow-lg">
                <div class="flex items-start gap-6 mb-6">
                  <div class="bg-primary/10 p-3 rounded-lg">
                    <svg class="w-8 h-8 text-primary" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                      <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M20 7l-8-4-8 4m16 0l-8 4m8-4v10l-8 4m0-10L4 7m8 4v10M4 7v10l8 4"/>
                    </svg>
                  </div>
                  <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold">Defining and Validating MVPs</h3>
                </div>
                <p class="text-gray-600 mb-6">
                  Address the unique challenges of hardware MVP development and validation.
                </p>
                <ul class="space-y-3 text-gray-600 mb-6">
                  <li>• Determine minimal feature sets</li>
                  <li>• Master rapid prototyping techniques</li>
                  <li>• Balance technical feasibility with user needs</li>
                  <li>• Optimize manufacturing considerations</li>
                </ul>
                <p class="text-sm text-gray-500">Duration: 3 days</p>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>

          <div class="text-center">
            <a
              href="/contact"
              class="inline-block bg-primary text-white px-8 py-4 rounded-lg font-medium hover:bg-primary/90 transition-colors"
            >
              Enroll in Training Today
            </a>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>
  </main>

  <Footer />
</Layout>